display_long_description:
**"A must-have for Quest"** - UploadVR 🎖️

**"Breathes new life into an old game"** - MIXED News 🎖️

**"Gets your adrenaline pumping"** - 6DOF Reviews 🎖️

# - ENTER THE WAR ROOM -
Defend your airspace in thrilling tabletop mixed reality!

Manage your city's defenses and protect your citizens by thwarting enemy attacks with carefully timed retaliatory strikes.

[media]

# - ACQUIRE UPGRADES -
If your Headquarters survives the onslaught, you'll be rewarded with new turrets and discretionary funds to spend on upgrades and reconstruction.

[media]

# - FACE MOUNTING CHALLENGES -
As you survive past early levels, you'll encounter increasingly fierce opposition. Will you achieve eternal glory on the leaderboards, or will your city fall under siege? The fate of your airspace rests in your hands!

[media]

# - KEY FEATURES -
- Game Modes: Training, Practice and Arcade
- 6 Training Maps; 7 Practice Maps; 2 Arcade Maps with Leaderboards
- 8 Turret types, 5 Enemy types
- 15 Turret Contracts (i.e. bounties/mini-quests)
- Different color palettes, pause system, tabletop repositioning
- And more being added every month...

Join our Discord to share your feedback on the development roadmap!
